criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18-64 years old;

          -  Nursing Diagnosis "Anxiety" (according to ICNP/NANDA standardized nursing language) -
             assessment using NOC outcome "Anxiety Level" (Portuguese version);

          -  Elementary education (completed).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Being in therapy provided by a psychologist (at the moment of the session 0);

          -  Severe cognitive deficit (assessment using Mini-Mental State Examination);

          -  Intellectual disability;

          -  Confusional state;

          -  Severe delusions and/or hallucinations;

          -  Psychomotor agitation.
